seller.description: Hi, my name is Adven Kristian. I am creating surf, skate, BMX, snowboard, extreme sports, and streetwear apparel and logo design. I am an experienced graphic designer with many years of experience in design and brand identity. I am a great communicator and have the ability to provide extremely fast turnaround times. My goal as your designer is to deliver a finished product that you love - a product that is edgy, unique, and most importantly effective in delivering your message. Feel free to contact me with any questions! Cheers!
